### Create a New Payment
POST http://localhost:8000/api/payments
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "phone": "0722227154",
  "amount": 5000,
  "status": "pending",
  "transactionId": "MPESA123456789",
  "merchantRequestId": "MERCHANT123",
  "checkoutRequestId": "CHECKOUT456"
}

### Get All Payments
GET http://localhost:8000/api/payments
Content-Type: application/json

### Get a Single Payment by ID
GET http://localhost:8000/api/payments/1
Content-Type: application/json

### Update a Payment (Change Status)
PATCH http://localhost:8000/api/payments/1
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "status": "completed",
  "transactionId": "MPESA987654321"
}

### Delete a Payment
DELETE http://localhost:8000/api/payments/1
Content-Type: application/json
